---
title: Oven Baked Lemon Salmon and Caper Dill Salsa with Beetroot, Feta Peashoot Salad and Crushed Potatoes
description: We love a good Lemon Salmon and Caper Dill Salsa and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/oven-baked-lemon-salmon-and-caper-dill-salsa-e3896644-1520927d.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/oven-baked-lemon-salmon-and-caper-dill-salsa-5ed8b34dc6d58421224fda32-407b2d50.pdf
